  
mvn clean: Deletes the target directory, removing all previously built artifacts
mvn compile: Compiles the source code located in src/main/java
mvn test: Runs unit tests using a framework like JUnit or TestNG.
mvn package: Compiles, tests, and bundles the code into a distributable format like a JAR or WAR file
mvn verify: Runs integration tests and checks to ensure the package meets quality criteria.
mvn deploy: Copies the final package to a remote repository for sharing with other developers.
